        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3028070759" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer18096209024872090858"><b>
  <i>
    <s>“Racism sucks, inn&apos;t? It’s kind of fucking shit”-Daniel Kaluuya 2018</s>
  </i>
</b><br/><img src='https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/hostedimages/1576094124i/28596158.jpg' width='330' height='200' alt='description' class='gr-hostedUserImg'/><br/><br/><br/>Liiiisteen… the movie is better. It’s obviously an interesting read but some times it’s extremely slow and boring. There are things that just don’t have to be constantly explained in detail.<br/><br/><b>
  <i>‘’I had not then learned the measure of &quot;man&apos;s inhumanity to man,&quot; nor to what limitless extent of wickedness he will go for the love of gain’’</i>
</b><br/>Slave owners treated slaves like animals…some of them treated them worse than anima</span>
  <span id="freeText18096209024872090858" style="display:none"><b>
  <i>
    <s>“Racism sucks, inn't? It’s kind of fucking shit”-Daniel Kaluuya 2018</s>
  </i>
</b><br><img src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/hostedimages/1576094124i/28596158.jpg" width="330" height="200" alt="description" class="gr-hostedUserImg"><br><br><br>Liiiisteen… the movie is better. It’s obviously an interesting read but some times it’s extremely slow and boring. There are things that just don’t have to be constantly explained in detail.<br><br><b>
  <i>‘’I had not then learned the measure of "man's inhumanity to man," nor to what limitless extent of wickedness he will go for the love of gain’’</i>
</b><br>Slave owners treated slaves like animals…some of them treated them worse than animals. How fucked up do you have to be to own a person and treat them like shit just so you can make some money? <br><br>Solomon shows us two types of slave owners, the ‘’good’’ and the abominable. Yes not beating the shit out of someone is great and all but you still kidnapped a person. Both of them are pretty much on the same of level of fuckery.</span>
  <a data-text-id="18096209024872090858" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

